25:26.274 --> 25:27.776
[grunting]

25:35.659 --> 25:38.245
[grunting]

25:50.715 --> 25:52.634
[growls]

25:53.969 --> 25:56.179
[roaring]

26:01.559 --> 26:03.895
[groans]

26:07.107 --> 26:08.483
[grunts]

26:12.279 --> 26:13.863
[screeching]

26:17.117 --> 26:18.285
[groans]

26:20.954 --> 26:23.581
- [growls]
- [screaming]

26:27.043 --> 26:29.004
[scientists clamoring]

26:29.004 --> 26:30.088
[Dr. Myers] Who are you?

26:32.590 --> 26:34.801
[growling softly]

26:34.801 --> 26:36.886
This is a restricted area.

26:45.812 --> 26:47.230
They're all dead.

26:47.230 --> 26:48.857
Not all of them.

26:48.857 --> 26:51.526
[Dr. Myers] You need to leave
right now.

26:52.319 --> 26:53.820
Djuba is coming home.

26:53.820 --> 26:57.032
No, this animal isn't
going anywhere.

26:57.032 --> 26:58.533
It's highly contagious.

26:58.533 --> 27:02.037
Because of you. Now, go.

27:02.037 --> 27:04.789
You need to listen to reason.

27:04.789 --> 27:09.252
It is carrying
a mutant Anthrax bacillus.

27:11.046 --> 27:12.505
What did you do to her?

27:12.505 --> 27:14.758
She is a test subject.

27:14.758 --> 27:18.636
Are you familiar
with the symptoms
of anthrax infections?

27:20.347 --> 27:21.765
[Dr. Myers] Mmm.

27:21.765 --> 27:24.351
They usually begin
with red swelling
at the site

27:24.351 --> 27:27.354
where the bacillus
gains entry into the body.

27:27.354 --> 27:31.149
This is followed
by listlessness,
headaches, ulcers,

27:31.149 --> 27:37.322
internal bleeding, convulsions,
and ultimately,
of course, death.

27:37.322 --> 27:40.742
You release this animal
and every other living creature

27:40.742 --> 27:44.746
that comes into contact with it
is in serious danger.

27:44.746 --> 27:48.416
This could spread across
the continent in weeks.

27:49.459 --> 27:51.252
We can't take her out of here.

27:52.087 --> 27:53.254
[Dr. Myers] That's right.

27:54.631 --> 27:58.760
It is dying right here
on this table.

28:00.887 --> 28:01.763
Dominic...

28:03.807 --> 28:05.600
I am The Beast.

28:13.024 --> 28:16.653
And you are correct, Dr. Myers.

28:17.654 --> 28:22.200
This ape, my friend.

28:22.200 --> 28:24.452
She is going to die here.

28:25.662 --> 28:28.331
But you will die with her.

28:29.290 --> 28:32.252
No. Wait. No, no!

28:32.252 --> 28:33.628
[Dr. Myers grunts]

28:34.671 --> 28:36.631
You're going to be together.

28:38.508 --> 28:39.509
[Dr. Myers groans]

28:46.349 --> 28:47.350
[Dr. Myers] No.

28:51.855 --> 28:53.106
[gagging]

28:54.899 --> 28:56.025
[grunts]

29:07.620 --> 29:08.955
This was his lab?

29:11.291 --> 29:12.208
No.

29:14.878 --> 29:17.422
Dr. Myers worked
for someone else.

29:42.405 --> 29:43.490
[Gar sighs]

30:11.726 --> 30:13.144
[Dominic] It was his lab.

30:17.690 --> 30:19.275
Dr. Niles Caulder.

30:21.653 --> 30:23.071
You knew all of this?

30:29.118 --> 30:30.828
[breathing heavily]

30:37.293 --> 30:39.879
He released Sakutia on purpose.

30:41.506 --> 30:43.883
[thrumming]

30:58.565 --> 31:00.066
[Gar] What happened?

31:00.066 --> 31:03.319
You have been in The Red up
until this very moment.

31:05.154 --> 31:06.948
What?

31:06.948 --> 31:09.742
[Dominic] Everything here
already happened.

31:12.453 --> 31:15.373
I destroyed this lab.

31:17.166 --> 31:18.042
Years ago.

31:19.669 --> 31:23.423
Then, what has all
of this been?

31:26.342 --> 31:30.722
The cave? The men with guns?

31:32.515 --> 31:34.267
An illusion?

31:34.267 --> 31:36.436
An echo of the past.

31:37.562 --> 31:39.147
To show you.

31:39.147 --> 31:45.778
That the man
who saved my life
killed my mother and father?

31:45.778 --> 31:52.160
And many others,
justified by his quest
to unlock eternal life.

31:55.872 --> 31:59.334
What does immortality
have to do with
re-engineering a virus?

32:00.501 --> 32:01.502
Mmm.

32:04.088 --> 32:09.260
All life is tied to The Red.

32:09.260 --> 32:12.805
Dr. Caulder attempted
to tap into it.

32:12.805 --> 32:17.268
He released the virus
knowing dozens would die.

32:17.268 --> 32:20.021
But he only needed one to live.

32:21.689 --> 32:26.194
Another test subject
for his Doom Patrol.

32:28.321 --> 32:30.782
Then why not just tell me
all of this?

32:33.034 --> 32:37.830
People in your life are never
who you think them to be.

32:37.830 --> 32:42.335
They can be destructive
at worst, like Dr. Caulder,

32:42.335 --> 32:45.421
or a distraction at best,
like the Titans.

32:48.716 --> 32:53.513
You... are so much more

32:53.513 --> 32:57.975
than their Beast Boy, Gar.

32:59.811 --> 33:01.688
You are the changeling.

33:02.814 --> 33:04.691
The true protector of The Red,

33:04.691 --> 33:07.694
ready to release me
from my duties.

33:08.903 --> 33:11.447
I have sought you out
for many years...

33:12.949 --> 33:14.283
and now you are here.

33:16.703 --> 33:17.537
At last.

33:23.710 --> 33:24.711
I'm leaving.

33:27.755 --> 33:29.090
No.

33:29.090 --> 33:30.925
You have a responsibility.

33:30.925 --> 33:32.719
I know I do.

33:32.719 --> 33:35.638
You've wasted my time.
My friends' lives,
they might be in danger.

33:35.638 --> 33:38.391
Maybe the whole world.
You have no idea
the evil we're up against.

33:38.391 --> 33:41.144
Protecting The Red
is your destiny!

33:41.144 --> 33:42.603
You know that, Gar.
You saw it.

33:44.230 --> 33:48.109
You are meant to fight alone,
to be alone.

33:48.109 --> 33:51.904
The avatar of The Red
is above family or friends.

33:51.904 --> 33:54.490
You have sought them out,

33:54.490 --> 33:56.909
but you cannot have them.

33:56.909 --> 34:00.163
Your role in this world
is too great, too important.

34:00.163 --> 34:04.167
- Stop.
- I speak only the truth.

34:04.167 --> 34:07.336
The truth you saw and see.

34:08.504 --> 34:09.422
I know...

34:10.506 --> 34:14.719
how lonely a life
of solitude is,

34:16.387 --> 34:19.432
but you must give your heart
to it all.

34:19.432 --> 34:21.142
Stop talking, please.

34:21.142 --> 34:25.563
To The Red and no one else.

34:33.196 --> 34:38.618
The Red is supposed
to connect me to
every single living creature

34:38.618 --> 34:39.660
on Earth, right?

34:40.286 --> 34:41.954
Yes.

34:41.954 --> 34:44.791
Then not only am I not alone,

34:46.250 --> 34:50.546
but I'm connected
to everybody on the planet.

34:52.799 --> 34:55.051
The Red chose me
to be its protector, fine.

34:56.135 --> 34:58.638
I'm in. I'll do it.

34:58.638 --> 34:59.764
[chuckles]

35:02.099 --> 35:05.561
But I will not abandon
the people I love most.

35:07.063 --> 35:09.941
I'm going to them now,

35:09.941 --> 35:13.319
and then we're gonna
save the world together.

35:13.319 --> 35:16.155
You cannot traverse
The Red like this yet.

35:16.155 --> 35:17.782
Time and space.

35:17.782 --> 35:19.200
You are not ready.

35:19.200 --> 35:23.788
For the first time
in my life, I know I am.

35:25.790 --> 35:27.875
- [thrumming]
- [Dominic] Wait!

35:33.631 --> 35:34.507
[yelps]

35:35.675 --> 35:36.884
[grunts]

35:42.265 --> 35:44.016
[young Gar crying]

35:51.357 --> 35:53.317
I don't wanna be alone. [sobs]

36:18.134 --> 36:18.968
No.

36:20.595 --> 36:24.348
You're not.
You're gonna find friends.

36:25.641 --> 36:26.726
You're gonna find family...

36:30.354 --> 36:34.066
and they are going to love you
as much as you love them.

36:34.066 --> 36:40.573
Okay? You are never, ever
going to be alone again.

36:41.866 --> 36:43.284
I promise.

